		   		<h3>Design & Build</h3>	
		   			<p></p>	
		   			<div>
						<p>I'm a UX Designer based in Bristol and I do freelance projects. With an enthusiasm and experience in designing interfaces for UX/Usability and designing Information Architecture, I'm currently designing and building websites for a range of businesses that includes a catering, a natural beauty products, and a registered 'not for profit' company who provide computer networking services and training.</p>
						<p>I enjoy being highly creative and keeping up-to-date with design/usability testing. Completed an MSc (merit) Software Development (IT) degree at UWE, including a UWE internship completing research in Persuasive Design, as well as designing for usability/usability testing working as a UWE intern on the MOBISERV research project at the BRL (Bristol Robotics Laboratory). http://www.brl.ac.uk/researchprojects/mobiservproject.aspx  My experience in designing for user experience/usability includes:</p> 		
